        "text": "You channel powerful electric current through the metal of a weapon, zapping anyone the item hits. The target becomes a *+1 shock* weapon. If any target of an attack with the weapon is wearing metal armor or is primarily made of metal, the electricity damage die from the *shock* rune is 1d12.",
